translations: v．恳求，祈求：向某人或某事表示强烈的请求或祈求。

sentences.sentence: The best deal is of course an alpha who is also a provider, but those things kinda cancel each other out because an alpha stops being an alpha when he supplicates.
sentences.translation: 理想的情况当然是，上等男人同时也是供养者，不过这两者事实上有点冲突，一旦上等男人开始乞怜，他就不再是上等男人。
